<paragraph id="7D5CCDA62AFC6F77E6A75A07C08F81ED" pageNumber="27">- (Pl. 2, fig. 24). - [[ worker ]]. Fusca, thorace pedibusque dilutioribus, copiose, hand longe pilosa, capite thoraceque grosse reticulatis, minus nitidis, abdomine, excepto pedunculo, nitidissima, punctato, pro-mesonoti disco transverso, angulis anticis acutis, postice obtuse 6 - lobato, metanoto sine spinis, pedunculi nodis cuneiformibus. - Long. 2 - 2 1 / 4 mill. - Makapan.</paragraph>
